text: Seminella is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Columbellidae, the dove snails. ==Species== Species within the genus Seminella include: * Seminella comistea (Melvill, 1906) * Seminella peasei (Martens & Langkavel, 1871) * Seminella roseotincta (Hervier, 1899) * Seminella virginea (Gould, 1860) ==References== Category:Columbellidae
title: Seminella
